							<div id="pum_popup_title_5160" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Nabatanzi Miriam			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>Nabatanzi Miriam is a seasoned advocate with vast experience in regulatory compliance, family and corporate law practice, and strategic risk management. She has represented URSB in complex civil cases, and Uganda in criminal matters. Miriam has led a number of successful reforms and projects at URSB.<br />
Miriam holds a master’s degree in law, along with professional qualifications in Leadership, Intellectual Property Rights, Secured Transactions, Governance, Risk and Compliance, Quality Management Systems, Anti Money Laundering and Terrorism Financing, Investigations and Prosecutions, among other certifications.</p>
		</div>

				
