							<div id="pum_popup_title_2652" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of CPA Ambrose Ekaju			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>5th Floor, Uganda Business Facilitation Centre,<br />
Plot 1 Baskerville Avenue, Kololo,<br />
P. O. Box 6848, Kampala.</p>
<p>He is passionate, experienced, reputable and highly professional Accountant with thorough knowledge in Internal Audit, Financial Management, Risk Management and Good Leadership skills.</p>
<p>Ambrose has been a member of Institute of Certified Public Accountants of Uganda (ICPAU) for over 10 Years and has served as a member of Public Practice Panel (2018-2020), a member of Internal Audit Panel (2020- 2022) both are sub committees of the Professional Standards Committee of the ICPAU.</p>
<p>Previously he served as Manager Internal Audit at URSB from 2015- 2021, Head of internal Audit at Soroti Municipal Council (2007-2015) and Internal Auditor at Soroti Municipal Council (2005-2007). Ambrose holds CPA-U, PGD in Financial Management of UMI, BBA(Accounts) of Ndejje university, Diploma in Project Planning and Management among others.</p>
		</div>

				
