	<div id="popmake-2612" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2612" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Arthur Kwesiga			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p><!--
<i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> <b>Email:</b> <a href="mailto: akwesiga@ursb.go.ug">akwesiga@ursb.go.ug</a>
--></p>
<p>4th Floor, Uganda Business Facilitation Centre,<br />
Plot 1 Baskerville Avenue, Kololo,<br />
P. O. Box 6848, Kampala.</p>
<p>Arthur Kwesiga is a seasoned professional with over 20 years of experience in the ICT and Public Sector Service industry. He holds diverse educational qualifications, including Master&#8217;s Degrees in International Business Administration and Information Technology, a Masters of Laws in Patent and Design Law, and a Bachelor&#8217;s Degree in Computer Science. His expertise encompasses areas such as ICT, Commercial Registries, Leadership, and Financial Management.</p>
<p>Arthur has been instrumental in implementing business, intellectual property and civil registration reforms, driving public service delivery with digital technologies, and coordinating cost-effective systems for e-government initiatives.</p>
<p>A certified Project Manager and Lead Auditor/Implementer in Quality Management Systems, he has a proven track record of successfully managing ICT projects, innovating products and services to meet customer needs, and maintaining organizational quality standards. His achievements include spearheading commercial registry reform projects, enhancing public service through technology, exhibiting proficient project management, and upholding high-quality standards within various organizations.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
	id="pum-2606" 
	role="dialog" 
	aria-modal="false"
	aria-labelledby="pum_popup_title_2606"
	class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-2376 pum-theme-default-theme popmake-overlay click_open" 
	data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:2606,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;profile-of-caroline-tusingwire-egesa-2&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:2376,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;cookie_name&quot;:[&quot;pum-2606&quot;],&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:false,&quot;esc_press&quot;:false,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}">

