	<div id="popmake-2536" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2536" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Mr. Masagazi Deogratious			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mr. Masagazi is a seasoned public service administrator with over two decades of progressive service across Uganda&#8217;s central government institutions, including the Office of the President, the Office of the Prime Minister, and the Ministry of Trade, Industry, and Cooperatives. He brings a demonstrated record of executive-level administrative leadership, strategic coordination, and institutional management, with formal academic training in public administration and the social sciences.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mr. Masagazi believes in a results-oriented approach to governance, with competencies in strategic planning, budget and financial management, human resource evaluation, and inter-ministerial coordination. He holds a Master of Public Administration and Management from Uganda Management Institute, a Postgraduate Diploma in Public Administration from Uganda Management Institute and a Bachelor of Arts in Social Sciences (Sociology) from Makerere University.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
	id="pum-2534" 
	role="dialog" 
	aria-modal="false"
