	class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-2376 pum-theme-default-theme popmake-overlay click_open" 
	data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:2534,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;profile-of-ms-mercy-k-kainobwisho&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:2376,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;cookie_name&quot;:[&quot;pum-2534&quot;],&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:false,&quot;esc_press&quot;:false,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}">

	<div id="popmake-2534" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2534" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Ms. Mercy K. Kainobwisho			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>5th Floor, Uganda Business Facilitation Centre,<br />
Plot 1 Baskerville Avenue, Kololo,<br />
P. O. Box 6848, Kampala.</p>
<p>Ms. Mercy K. Kainobwisho is the Registrar General and Official Receiver of the Uganda Registration Services Bureau since December 2020. She is an Advocate of Courts of Judicature with vast experience in Intellectual Property Law, Business Law, Project Management, Oil and Gas Law, Leadership and General Management. She holds a Masters of Laws in Intellectual Property from University of Turin, Italy; a Master of Business Administration (MBA) from Makerere University Business School, Post Graduate Diploma in Legal Practice from the Law Development Center, and a Bachelor of Laws degree from Makerere University.</p>
<p>She is the sitting Vice-Chair of the World Intellectual Property Organization’s (WIPO) General Assembly and the WIPO Seventeenth Advisory Committee on Enforcement (ACE) sessions. She is also very passionate about mentoring young people into leadership among other things.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
	id="pum-2532" 
	role="dialog" 
	aria-modal="false"
	aria-labelledby="pum_popup_title_2532"
	class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-2376 pum-theme-default-theme popmake-overlay click_open" 
	data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:2532,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;profile-of-ms-tereza-namwach&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:2376,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;cookie_name&quot;:[&quot;pum-2532&quot;],&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:false,&quot;esc_press&quot;:false,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}">

	<div id="popmake-2532" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2532" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Ms. Tereza Namwach			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>Ms. Tereza Namwach is a qualified professional currently serving as Assistant Commissioner for Finance and Planning, in the Ministry of Finance Planning and Economic Development (MoFPED). She has a robust educational background, including a Master of Arts Degree in Economic Policy and Planning and a Bachelor of Arts in Development Economics from Makerere University. With an impressive 14-year career trajectory within MoFPED, she has risen through the ranks from Economist/Finance Officer to her current position of Assistant Commissioner, Finance and Planning.</p>
<p>Ms. Tereza&#8217;s expertise lies in public sector planning, budgeting, and financial management, coupled with proficiency in policy formulation, and appraisal of economic functions. Her skills extend to IT proficiency in Government financial management systems and other computer applications. Her significant contribution to national budget reforms and experience as a Budget Analyst for key government sectors/programmes underscore her strategic mindset and ability to align financial processes with organizational objectives.</p>
<p>Beyond MoFPED, her involvement in bodies such as the Busitema University Council showcases her experience in Board operations, further enhancing her capabilities. With a deep mastery of the principles of public financial management, Tereza is well-equipped to play a crucial oversight role in fostering proper corporate governance across various sectors.</p>
<p>Ms. Tereza Namwach&#8217;s qualifications, extensive experience, and proven leadership make her a valuable asset for contributing to maintaining high standards of corporate governance as well as achievement of its strategic objectives.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
	id="pum-2530" 
	role="dialog" 
	aria-modal="false"
	aria-labelledby="pum_popup_title_2530"
	class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-2376 pum-theme-default-theme popmake-overlay click_open" 
	data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:2530,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;profile-of-george-fred-kagimu&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:2376,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;cookie_name&quot;:[&quot;pum-2530&quot;],&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:false,&quot;esc_press&quot;:false,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}">

	<div id="popmake-2530" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2530" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of George Fred Kagimu			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>George Fred Kagimu, renowned for his significant contributions to Ugandan society, has left an indelible mark as a seasoned politician, accomplished businessman, and dedicated civic leader. His illustrious tenure as the Mayor of Mukono Municipality from 2016 to 2021 showcased his commitment to progress and community development.</p>
<p>George Fred Kagimu continues to be a prominent figure in the Mukono region, both as a thriving businessman and as a valuable member of the Uganda Registration Services Bureau (URSB) board since 2023.</p>
<p>Serving as Chairman of the Total Uganda Alumni Group since 2018, he actively fosters professional networks and collaboration.</p>
<p>In his role as Vice Chairman of the Uganda National Chamber of Commerce and Industries, he champions the interests of Ugandan businesses. Additionally, his ownership of Festino City in Mukono underscores his commitment to community enrichment. George Fred Kagimu&#8217;s multi-faceted leadership is an asset to Mukono and the nation.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
	id="pum-2528" 
	role="dialog" 
	aria-modal="false"
	aria-labelledby="pum_popup_title_2528"
	class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-2376 pum-theme-default-theme popmake-overlay click_open" 
	data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:2528,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;profile-of-ms-annie-ninkijuka-katushabe&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:2376,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;cookie_name&quot;:[&quot;pum-2528&quot;],&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:false,&quot;esc_press&quot;:false,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}">

	<div id="popmake-2528" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2528" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Ms. Annie Ninkijuka Katushabe			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>Annie is an accomplished business professional, experienced Human Resource and administration practitioner and a Managing Partner of Info Consults International Ltd, a Consultancy firm established in 2004 to provide solutions in Records Management, Document Management, Knowledge Management, Project Management and Information Technology.</p>
<p>Holds a Master of Business Administration (MBA) in Human Resource Management and certifications in Corporate Governance and Balanced Scorecard Strategic Management System among others.</p>
<p>Annie has over 20 years of Management experience across various domains, having previously worked at AMPROC INC and Uganda Telecom, where she demonstrated expertise in leading teams to deliver strategic results and organizational success.</p>
<p>Her current pursuit is the digitalization of business processes to enhance service delivery in both public and private sectors. Noteworthy, she has provided strategic leadership for the conceptualization, design, development and successful deployment of a state-of-the-art Electronic Document and Records Management System (eDocs+), an innovation that will revolutionalise the management of records and documents across the Government of Uganda.</p>
<p>She is an avid reader of leadership, business and management literature; a health &amp; fitness enthusiast and a Rotarian, committed to uplifting the quality of life of the vulnerable and less privileged in society.</p>
		</div>

				
							<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
			x			</button>
		
	</div>

</div>
<div 
