	<div id="popmake-2526" class="pum-container popmake theme-2376 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">

				
							<div id="pum_popup_title_2526" class="pum-title popmake-title">
				Profile of Mr. Byaruhanga Alex			</div>
		
		
				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<p>Mr. Byaruhanga Alex is an experienced litigation lawyer, Researcher and Legislative Counsel with excellent knowledge of legal reform, policy reform and formulation with advanced skills in statutory interpretation and legislative process both Principal legislation and Subsidiary legislation. He is an Advocate of the High Court, Principal State Attorney, Office of the First Parliamentary Counsel, Ministry of Justice and Constitutional Affairs / Attorney General’s Chambers. He is a member of East African Law Society and Uganda Law Society since 2014.</p>
		</div>

				
